{"TopicId":168908,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Can I Move HUD Items Around?","CreatedByName":"Flexico","CreatedById":168681,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-25T23:28:57Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Flexico","CreatedById":168681,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-25T23:28:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI find the navball right in the middle tends to obscure my view, so I\u0027d like to move it to the lower right and move the crew facecams to the upper left. Is there a way to do this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-25T23:32:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223252755\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168908\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221514244537\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022168681\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Flexico\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Flexico said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI find the navball right in the middle tends to obscure my view, so I\u0027d like to move it to the lower right and move the crew facecams to the upper left. Is there a way to do this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere is a slider bar in the options menu for moving the Navball left and right. That\u0027s about it though really.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI suggest moving it to the far left, by the staging display.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can also toggle the facecams to hidden by pushing the little arrow next to them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Flexico","CreatedById":168681,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-25T23:43:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAaahhh, moving the navball to the left was perfect. Thank you!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-12-26T00:25:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223252764\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022168908\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221514245386\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022168681\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Flexico\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n41 minutes ago, Flexico said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAaahhh, moving the navball to the left was perfect. Thank you!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnytime!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}